title: Catalans declare independence from Spain in historic vote
description:
Spanish Prime Minister Mariano Rajoy just moved to dissolve Catalonia's parliament a few hours after it voted to become totally independent from the rest of the country. Thousands had gathered in Barcelona to celebrate, but now the mood has changed. RT's Charlotte Dubenskij has the details.
